high_descs: Turn left a little bit, walk pass the bath tub to go to the first sink you see and look up to the mirror.
Grab the hand towel next to the mirror.
Turn around, walk towards the wall and turn to the bath tub.
Put the towel inside the bath tub.
Walk to the left towards the wall and turn right to go to another sink with a yellow cloth inside it. Look up to the mirror.
Take the hand towel that is hanging near the wall next to the mirror.
Turn around and go to the left to go back to the bath tub.
Put the hand towel inside the bath tub as well.
anns.task_desc: Put 2 bath towel hanging near the mirror to the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn around, take a step forward, and turn right towards the towel holder on the wall in front of you.
Take the towel from the holder.
Turn right to face the tub.
Place the towel in the tub.
Turn around and walk towards the towel holder on the wall next to the sink.
Pick up the towel from the holder.
Turn around and walk towards the tub.
Place the towel in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Transfer the towels on the towel holders into the tub.

high_descs: Turn to your left walk few steps then turn to your right head towards the side of the sink
Pick up the cloth from the rack on the wall
Turn around to your left then make few steps going to the tub
Drop the cloth on the tub
Turn to your left cross the room then turn to your right facing the sink
Pick up the cloth on the rack hanging on the wall
Turn to your right and head to the tub
Drop the cloth beside the left side of the other cloth in the tub
anns.task_desc: Put two cloth in the tub

high_descs: Turn around, hang a right at the end of the tub and head to the end of the vanity.
Pick up the white towel hanging from a steel ring to the right of the mirror.
Turn around, hang a left at the end of the tub, and turn left to face the tub.
Put the towel inside the tub in the middle.
Turn left, head to the wall and hang a right to reach the vanity.
Pick up the white towel hanging from a steel ring to the left of the mirror.
Turn around, hang a left at the toilet, walk towards the tub and turn left to face the tub.
Put the white towel to the left of the middle towel inside the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place two towels into a tub.

high_descs: Turn left, walk around bathtub toward sink, face towel on ring on wall to right of sink.
Take towel from ring.
Turn left, left again,  walk to tub, turn left to face it.
Put towel into bathtub.
Turn left, walk to wall, turn right, go to sink.
Take towel from ring on wall to left of sink.
Turn right, turn right again, walk to toilet, turn left, go to tub.
Put towel into tub.
